# Spotify App Configuration
# Get these values from https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard

# Your Spotify App Client ID
VITE_CLIENT_ID=your_spotify_client_id_here

# Your Spotify App Redirect URI (should match what you set in Spotify dashboard)
# For local development, use: http://localhost:5174
VITE_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:5174

# Instructions:
# 1. Go to https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
# 2. Create a new app (or use existing one)
# 3. Copy your Client ID and paste it above
# 4. Add your redirect URI to the app settings (should match VITE_REDIRECT_URI)
# 5. Save this file as .env (remove .example from filename)
